<div class="music-list" style="margin-top:20px;"><div class="music-wrap clear"><dl class="clear"><dt><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/08/daydreaming-1.php"><img src="http://focussound.jp/review/upload/daydreaming.jpg" alt="Daydreaming / Rafael Anton Irisarri" /></a></dt><dd><h4><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/08/daydreaming-1.php">Daydreaming<br />Rafael Anton Irisarri</a></h4><p>アメリカのシアトル在住のアーティスト「Rafael Anton Irisarri」の作品。静粛な雰囲気にゆったりとしたピアノが美しい作品。読書しながら自分だけの世界に浸ることができます。</p><div class="buy"><a href="http://www.amazon.co.jp/gp/product/B000N6TZJI?ie=UTF8&tag=bootscafe-22&linkCode=as2&camp=247&creative=1211&creativeASIN=B000N6TZJI" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'Amazon', 'Daydreaming-Rafael Anton Irisarri']);" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/amazon.gif" height="18" alt="amazonで買う" /></a>&nbsp;<a href="http%253A%252F%252Fitunes.apple.com%252Fjp%252Falbum%252Fdaydreaming%252Fid309466661%253Fuo%253D4%2526partnerId%253D30" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'iTunes', 'Daydreaming-Rafael Anton Irisarri']);" name="submit" value="{$button_text['send']}" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/itunes.gif" height="18" alt="iTunesで買う" /></a></div></dd></dl><dl class="clear"><dt><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/08/nuage.php"><img src="http://focussound.jp/review/upload/nuage.jpg" alt="Nuage / Sylvain Chauveau" /></a></dt><dd><h4><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/08/nuage.php">Nuage<br />Sylvain Chauveau</a></h4><p>美しいストリングスやピアノが素晴らしい作品。曲の長さが短いものが多く、場面ごとに気持ちを切り替えるような小説などに合うかもしれません。</p><div class="buy"><a href="http://www.amazon.co.jp/gp/product/B000YXMMBI?ie=UTF8&tag=bootscafe-22&linkCode=as2&camp=247&creative=1211&creativeASIN=B000YXMMBI" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'Amazon', 'Nuage-Sylvain Chauveau']);" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/amazon.gif" height="18" alt="amazonで買う" /></a>&nbsp;<a href="http%253A%252F%252Fitunes.apple.com%252Fjp%252Falbum%252Fnuage%252Fid276301072%253Fuo%253D4%2526partnerId%253D30" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'iTunes', 'Nuage-Sylvain Chauveau']);" name="submit" value="{$button_text['send']}" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/itunes.gif" height="18" alt="iTunesで買う" /></a></div></dd></dl></div><div class="music-wrap clear"><dl class="clear"><dt><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/08/gradation.php"><img src="http://focussound.jp/review/upload/graduation.jpg" alt="Gradation / LisM" /></a></dt><dd><h4><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/08/gradation.php">Gradation<br />LisM</a></h4><p>柔らかくて暖かみのあるサウンドが特徴の作品。気持ちを穏やかにしてくれるような雰囲気を持ったアルバムです。</p><div class="buy"><a href="http://www.amazon.co.jp/gp/product/B0035IVG84?ie=UTF8&tag=bootscafe-22&linkCode=as2&camp=247&creative=1211&creativeASIN=B0035IVG84" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'Amazon', 'Gradation-LisM']);" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/amazon.gif" height="18" alt="amazonで買う" /></a>&nbsp;<a href="http%253A%252F%252Fitunes.apple.com%252Fjp%252Falbum%252Fgradation%252Fid358127711%253Fuo%253D4%2526partnerId%253D30" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'iTunes', 'Gradation-LisM']);" name="submit" value="{$button_text['send']}" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/itunes.gif" height="18" alt="iTunesで買う" /></a></div></dd></dl><dl class="clear"><dt><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/08/variations-of-static.php"><img src="http://focussound.jp/review/upload/variations.jpg" alt="Variations of Static / Olafur Arnalds" /></a></dt><dd><h4><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/08/variations-of-static.php">Variations of Static<br />Olafur Arnalds</a></h4><p>ドラマチックな展開を持つ作品。美しいストリングスやピアノのサウンドの楽曲が多く、感情的な気分に浸らせてくれます。</p><div class="buy"><a href="http://www.amazon.co.jp/gp/product/B00189VNO4?ie=UTF8&tag=bootscafe-22&linkCode=as2&camp=247&creative=1211&creativeASIN=B00189VNO4" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'Amazon', 'Variations of Static-Olafur Arnalds']);" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/amazon.gif" height="18" alt="amazonで買う" /></a>&nbsp;<a href="http%253A%252F%252Fitunes.apple.com%252Fjp%252Falbum%252Fvariations-of-static-ep%252Fid281006870%253Fuo%253D4%2526partnerId%253D30" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'iTunes', 'Variations of Static-Olafur Arnalds']);" name="submit" value="{$button_text['send']}" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/itunes.gif" height="18" alt="iTunesで買う" /></a></div></dd></dl></div><div class="music-wrap clear"><dl class="clear"><dt><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/08/fordlandia.php"><img src="http://focussound.jp/review/upload/fordlandia.jpg" alt="Fordlandia / Johann Johannsson" /></a></dt><dd><h4><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/08/fordlandia.php">Fordlandia<br />Johann Johannsson</a></h4><p>映画を見ているような気分にさせてくれる作品。オーケストレーションが美しく、リピートして何度も聴きたくなります。</p><div class="buy"><a href="http://www.amazon.co.jp/gp/product/B001D45BSI?ie=UTF8&tag=bootscafe-22&linkCode=as2&camp=247&creative=1211&creativeASIN=B001D45BSI" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'Amazon', 'Fordlandia-Johann Johannsson']);" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/amazon.gif" height="18" alt="amazonで買う" /></a>&nbsp;<a href="http%253A%252F%252Fitunes.apple.com%252Fjp%252Falbum%252Fid293921148%253Fuo%253D4%2526partnerId%253D30" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'iTunes', 'Fordlandia-Johann Johannsson']);" name="submit" value="{$button_text['send']}" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/itunes.gif" height="18" alt="iTunesで買う" /></a></div></dd></dl><dl class="clear"><dt><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/08/post-piano.php"><img src="http://focussound.jp/review/upload/postpiano.jpg" alt="Post_Piano / Kenneth Kirschner & Taylor Deupree" /></a></dt><dd><h4><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/08/post-piano.php">Post_Piano<br />Kenneth Kirschner & Taylor Deupree</a></h4><p>まるで異次元に来てしまったような不思議な感覚を与えてくれる作品です。大きく形を変えたピアノの音が特徴の音楽です。</p><div class="buy"><a href="http://www.amazon.co.jp/gp/product/B00007BKHE?ie=UTF8&tag=bootscafe-22&linkCode=as2&camp=247&creative=1211&creativeASIN=B00007BKHE" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'Amazon', 'Post_Piano-Kenneth Kirschner & Taylor Deupree']);" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/amazon.gif" height="18" alt="amazonで買う" /></a>&nbsp;<a href="http%253A%252F%252Fitunes.apple.com%252Fjp%252Falbum%252Fpost-piano%252Fid301627562%253Fuo%253D4%2526partnerId%253D30" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'iTunes', 'Post_Piano-Kenneth Kirschner & Taylor Deupree']);" name="submit" value="{$button_text['send']}" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/itunes.gif" height="18" alt="iTunesで買う" /></a></div></dd></dl></div><div class="music-wrap clear"><dl class="clear"><dt><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/08/these-places-are-now-ruins.php"><img src="http://focussound.jp/review/upload/threeplacesarenow.jpg" alt="These Places Are Now Ruins / Last Days" /></a></dt><dd><h4><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/08/these-places-are-now-ruins.php">These Places Are Now Ruins<br />Last Days</a></h4><p>ギターやピアノなどのアコースティック楽器の響きの美しさを感じられる素晴らしい作品です。眠りにつく前に聴きたくなるような音楽です。</p><div class="buy"><a href="http://www.amazon.co.jp/gp/product/B000VKL0C6?ie=UTF8&tag=bootscafe-22&linkCode=as2&camp=247&creative=1211&creativeASIN=B000VKL0C6" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'Amazon', 'These Places Are Now Ruins-Last Days']);" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/amazon.gif" height="18" alt="amazonで買う" /></a>&nbsp;<a href="http%253A%252F%252Fitunes.apple.com%252Fjp%252Falbum%252Fthese-places-are-now-ruins%252Fid265987809%253Fuo%253D4%2526partnerId%253D30" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'iTunes', 'These Places Are Now Ruins-Last Days']);" name="submit" value="{$button_text['send']}" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/itunes.gif" height="18" alt="iTunesで買う" /></a></div></dd></dl><dl class="clear"><dt><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/08/the-echo-garden.php"><img src="http://focussound.jp/review/upload/echogarden.jpg" alt="The Echo Garden / Jimmy Behan" /></a></dt><dd><h4><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/08/the-echo-garden.php">The Echo Garden<br />Jimmy Behan</a></h4><p>孤独感を感じる作品。しかしながら優しさと柔らかさを持ち合わせており、1人の時間を心地よくさせてくれるようなアンビエントサウンドです。</p><div class="buy"><a href="http://www.amazon.co.jp/gp/product/B002ADQ29I?ie=UTF8&tag=bootscafe-22&linkCode=as2&camp=247&creative=1211&creativeASIN=B002ADQ29I" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'Amazon', 'The Echo Garden-Jimmy Behan']);" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/amazon.gif" height="18" alt="amazonで買う" /></a>&nbsp;<a href="http%253A%252F%252Fitunes.apple.com%252Fjp%252Falbum%252Fthe-echo-garden%252Fid307976088%253Fuo%253D4%2526partnerId%253D30" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'iTunes', 'The Echo Garden-Jimmy Behan']);" name="submit" value="{$button_text['send']}" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/itunes.gif" height="18" alt="iTunesで買う" /></a></div></dd></dl></div></div>

